DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20250912
DTSTAMP:20260424T230203Z
UID:94da1620-17c8-5f8b-a254-366d2e21f309
DESCRIPTION:Wednesday\, September 11\, is a federally-recognized National 
 Day of Service and Remembrance. Also known as 9/11 Day or Patriot Day\, th
 e designation encourages reflection on those who gave or risked their live
 s to serve others during the terrorist attacks in 2001\, and engagement in
  community service projects.
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
