 evident. In light of this\, schools across the nation are actively partici
 pating in Digital Citizenship Week\, which takes place from October 20 to 
 24. This special week serves as a reminder of the significance of digital 
 citizenship and the role it plays in molding responsible\, respectful\, an
 d empathetic online citizens. \n\nCheck out these resources for students 
 and learn more at commonsense.org.
