 ch 18\, 5:30-7:00 pm at the HSD Administration Center\,  Room 100\, 3038
  NE 49th Pl. Hillsboro\, OR 97124. Download the flyer here and please RSV
 P.During the March 18th\, and April 15th PAC meetings\, we will be creatin
 g ribbon skirts and shirts for our students. If you are interested in part
 icipating in making a ribbon skirt\, or adorning ribbon shirts for your st
 udent(s) for upcoming powwows\, please use the QR code on the invitation 
 for more information on how to participate. We look forward to seeing you 
 there! 
LOCATION:HSD Administration Center\, 3083 NE 49th Pl. Hillsboro\, Room 100
END:VEVENT
