DESCRIPTION:Between preparing delicious food\, adhering to strict nutritio
 n standards\, navigating student food allergies\, and offering service wit
 h a smile\, Hillsboro School District nutrition professionals have a lot o
 n their plate. To celebrate their hard work and commitment\, HSD schools w
 ill celebrate School Lunch Hero Day on May 1. School Lunch Hero Day provid
 es an opportunity for parents\, students\, school staff and communities to
  thank those who provide healthy meals to nearly 30 million of America’s
  students each school day.www.hsd.k12.or.us/nutrition
