BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Optimist Junior Golf Qualifier
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260523T123000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260523T170000
DTSTAMP:20260424T230204Z
UID:8d79c60f-995c-576f-aa79-322760a9307d
DESCRIPTION:The Optimist International Junior Golf Championship is one of 
 the largest and best-known junior golf tournaments in the world. Each year
 \, more than 600 golfers participate.The Optimist Club of Hillsboro\, Oreg
 on will conduct the 2026 Pacific Northwest (Oregon) Regional Qualifier Tou
 rnament.Optimists International has been involved in the sport of junior g
 olf for more than 30 years by holding local\, regional andinternational to
 urnaments.Players that qualify are eligible to compete in the Optimist Int
 ernational Jr Golf Tournament in Florida in July.Tournament: May 23\, 2026
 \, Saturday\, Sign-in 12:30-1:30pm\; Tee times start at 2pm.Location: Fore
 st Hills Golf Course\, 36260 SW Tongue Lane\, Cornelius\, Oregon 97113.Div
 isions: Boys 10-11\, 12-13\, 14-15\, 16-18\; Girls 10-12\, 13-14\, 15-18.E
 ntry Fee: $50.00.Contact Bruce Rumsch\, PNW Regional (Oregon) Tournament C
 oordinator for local registration form: padre19@comcast.net. Cell/text: 50
 3-341-9542.Advanced registration required. $1000 scholarships for the Inte
 rnational Tournament registration and expenses available for those that qu
 alify.Club email: HillsboroOptimistsClub@Gmail.comTournament Rules ONLINE:
  golf.optimist.org\; or search “Optimist International Jr Golf"REGISTER 
 ONLINE: golf.optimist.org under Pacific Northwest District (Oregon) Qualif
 ier AND mail the completed PNW Qualifier Form with payment to: Optimist Cl
 ub of Hillsboro Oregon\, PO Box 314\, Hillsboro\, OR 97123The Optimist Clu
 b of Hillsboro Oregon is a 501c3 nonprofit public charity.
LOCATION:Forest Hills Golf Course\, 36260 SW Tongue Lane\, Cornelius\, Ore
 gon 97113.
END:VEVENT
